Comment: 0,0:00:09.37,0:00:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,MAIN
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.37,0:00:29.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 花園多惠 你怎麼在這！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.85,0:00:31.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小歐……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.08,0:00:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不是小歐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.46,0:00:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們倆關係真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.25,0:00:37.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是 這傢伙自己上來的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.65,0:00:39.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼在這？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.25,0:00:42.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還想問你呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.31,0:00:45.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香澄呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.55,0:01:04.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃飯了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.22,0:01:08.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.83,0:01:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.24,0:01:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙綾你都幫我那麼多了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.60,0:01:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 吃早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.41,0:01:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不去學校嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.65,0:01:20.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.44,0:01:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文化祭你和香澄她們不是挺用心的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.13,0:01:28.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯……
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.61,0:01:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等會我和純他們去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.55,0:01:44.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 這個……
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.81,0:01:58.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了 就要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.67,0:01:59.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麵包還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.81,0:02:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.60,0:02:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飲料OK
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.09,0:02:04.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙綾還沒來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.37,0:02:06.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香澄 你回家了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.29,0:02:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.26,0:02:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麵包送過來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.25,0:02:11.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香澄 來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.61,0:02:13.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.84,0:02:15.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.25,0:02:17.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們來幫忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:19.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安……
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.28,0:02:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.48,0:02:22.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個挺重的 小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.23,0:02:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.03,0:02:27.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能麻煩簽個字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.91,0:02:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.61,0:02:33.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.75,0:02:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問 沙綾在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.55,0:02:41.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今早 妻子她……
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:47.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 沒大事的 以前她就是貧血體質
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.71,0:02:50.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女兒她非得帶妻子去醫院 就是不聽勸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.13,0:02:55.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你們添麻煩了 真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.20,0:02:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全沒有麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 能幫我告訴沙綾說這裡沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:06.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 她也有話想要告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.90,0:03:10.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保險起見 我們會給她做全面檢查的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.26,0:03:13.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但應該不會有大礙的哦 請放心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.26,0:03:17.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝文化祭辦得成功
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:23.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝演唱會辦得成功
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 來辦個最棒的文化祭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.68,0:03:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一定要讓它圓滿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備好哦 1-A 1-A 嘿嘿……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.64,0:03:49.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.07,0:03:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般不是喊 哦 的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:52.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.75,0:03:53.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.89,0:03:59.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1-A 1-A 嘿嘿喲！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:02.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1-A咖啡廳 正式開業
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨 歡迎光臨……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.78,0:04:17.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:19.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個麵包真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.30,0:04:21.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是山吹麵包房提供的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.62,0:04:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃得停不下來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.37,0:04:24.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特別推薦的是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 菠蘿麵包 奶油麵包 巧克力螺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.82,0:04:30.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅豆包 丹麥麵包……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.44,0:04:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.06,0:04:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是全部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.84,0:04:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.26,0:04:39.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做個鬼臉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.34,0:04:55.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會冷不防地見到姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.37,0:04:57.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明醬 好可愛！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.77,0:04:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊 明醬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.30,0:05:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.68,0:05:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要拍照囉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:04.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我跟爸爸借的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 說歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.56,0:05:08.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:13.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到達1-B
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.55,0:05:16.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有咲說她不知道自己班弄的什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.72,0:05:18.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這沒問題的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又失敗了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來人 有沒有能把我的女兒有咲公主逗樂的人在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.26,0:05:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.28,0:05:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別看啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.82,0:05:33.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有咲好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.99,0:05:35.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.18,0:05:40.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是衝著沒台詞很輕鬆這點才答應的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.64,0:05:41.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想死……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.76,0:05:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 有咲 很可愛的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.88,0:05:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快住手 我回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.13,0:05:49.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那演唱會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.83,0:05:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不管嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.94,0:05:57.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah 要來鬼屋轉轉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.74,0:06:00.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小麗學姐 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有真的鬼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.40,0:06:05.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個就請眼見為憑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.09,0:06:07.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就免了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.67,0:06:11.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文化祭上的鬼屋 充其量……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是扮家家酒那樣的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:17.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.63,0:06:19.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遇上了點交通事故
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.01,0:06:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 這是塗上去的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.53,0:06:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿 看著挺真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.77,0:06:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟是打算認真弄的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.69,0:06:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敷衍了事既沒成就感 也沒意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.49,0:06:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.11,0:06:35.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是 進不進來？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.98,0:07:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.09,0:07:11.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醫生都說沒事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.54,0:07:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有姐姐我在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:14.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文化祭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:18.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的 我陪你們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,豪華獎品是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:40.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你別把我暴露了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:43.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把這兩位打包回家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:45.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不提供這種服務……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.82,0:07:50.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香檳王 香檳王滿上！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.82,0:07:52.72,TopLeft,NTP,0,0,0,,註：此處的香檳王指唐培裡儂香檳王（{\fnFOT-Humming Std E\fs50}Dom Pérignon{\fn\fs}），平均每瓶價格243英鎊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.45,0:07:52.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學姐 這裡不提供這種服務
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.83,0:07:54.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狸貓？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:56.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本來想做的是熊貓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:07:58.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到做成奇怪的樣子了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.65,0:08:01.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別拍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.37,0:08:04.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乾杯 foo！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:07.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.89,0:08:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.73,0:08:44.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您有兩條語音留言
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:48.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙綾 我是香澄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.49,0:08:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你媽媽怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.49,0:08:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紗南有沒有哭呢 純純還精神嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.65,0:08:56.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙綾 你沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.53,0:09:02.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖啡廳辦得很成功 大家都很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:04.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顧客都說麵包很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有很多人打包帶走的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.04,0:09:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙綾 你在給沙綾打電話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.85,0:09:15.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎 嗨！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.04,0:09:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙綾  -這邊就交給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:18.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你媽媽怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.24,0:09:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,麵包很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.51,0:09:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,沙綾……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.04,0:09:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我給山吹麵包房作了首曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.27,0:09:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽聽看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.02,0:09:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家快停下！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.64,0:09:34.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二條語音留言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.06,0:09:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 這邊沒問題的 我們很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.39,0:09:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很開心 很開心 非常開心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.15,0:09:45.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以演唱會我們也會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.34,0:09:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會像能給沙綾聽到那樣拚盡全力的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.03,0:09:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 歌詞已經寄到你的家裡了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.02,0:09:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是沙綾和大家一起寫的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.29,0:09:57.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是不介意就看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.97,0:11:35.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香澄……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.17,0:11:41.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙綾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.46,0:11:47.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.21,0:11:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙綾真溫柔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.09,0:11:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對媽媽 對大家都那麼溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.43,0:12:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這份溫柔多分給自己一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.93,0:12:06.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.96,0:12:08.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙綾一定能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.47,0:12:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟你不是自己在堅持嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.86,0:12:19.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有紗南在呢 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.37,0:12:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.70,0:12:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.92,0:12:40.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺我真是太沒用了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.17,0:12:43.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.96,0:12:45.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.99,0:12:49.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.14,0:13:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝大家 下一支樂隊也要多多支持哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.54,0:13:15.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人來得好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.25,0:13:21.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.05,0:13:21.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.52,0:13:37.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要上前面去？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.52,0:13:38.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.09,0:13:46.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請讓我們試音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.21,0:13:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香澄！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.21,0:13:58.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.29,0:14:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好 我們是Poppin……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.07,0:14:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 難道一上來就是自我介紹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.17,0:14:07.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.01,0:14:12.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文化祭 大家玩得開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.88,0:14:17.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面獻上第一首曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:19.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《我的心像巧克力螺》
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.56,0:14:48.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好緊張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要什麼時候才能習慣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.84,0:14:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.37,0:15:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙綾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.42,0:15:14.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.02,0:15:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來是一首為了今天創作的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.65,0:15:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我們一起創作的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:23.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然今天有一個人不在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我們已經約好了總有一天要一起唱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.52,0:15:30.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然那一天還沒到來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.18,0:15:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我還是相信著的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.96,0:15:36.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我們能一起唱 一定可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:44.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏 文華 真結
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.54,0:15:45.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:47.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高興哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.88,0:15:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有沙綾在的樂隊 真的很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.06,0:15:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙綾你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.43,0:16:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.62,0:16:10.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常開心 非常喜歡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.29,0:16:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:17.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就說這些
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家還在等你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.45,0:16:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.14,0:16:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我們樂隊的新成員 裡實
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.47,0:16:31.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然害羞但是表演很華麗哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.08,0:16:33.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.67,0:16:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 那我借用一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.01,0:16:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 我們會用這樣的心情演唱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請大家欣賞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.25,0:17:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙綾……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.33,0:17:30.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.54,0:17:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.85,0:17:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我才聽過一遍 肯定是一團糟的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:37.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那剩下的就靠心意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.55,0:17:39.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.89,0:17:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨時可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家久等了 請欣賞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.67,0:18:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《STAR BEAT! ~星之鼓動~》
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.37,0:20:34.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是捏了把汗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.26,0:20:36.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清純Cute
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.87,0:20:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香澄！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.45,0:20:59.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.10,0:21:03.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來介紹樂隊成員
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.77,0:21:05.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍色吉他的多惠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.44,0:21:10.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貝斯手裡美
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.47,0:21:15.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊的是有咲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.99,0:21:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是鍵盤手！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.74,0:21:24.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鼓手……
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.76,0:21:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙綾！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.67,0:21:35.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Random Star 的戶山香澄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.69,0:21:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們五個人就是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.83,0:21:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Poppin' Party
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.23,0:23:18.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.72,0:23:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.25,0:23:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡就要停業了
